'''Tri-Nebula Entertainment''' was a media company owned by [[TriNebulon News/Legends|TriNebulon News]]. It was based in the [[Minos Cluster/Legends|Minos Cluster]].

==History==
Tri-Neb specialized in creating fantastic documentaries based only loosely on real events, combining both real [[Hologram/Legends|holographic]] footage and the work of their own artists. It was responsible for at least three stories concerning the adventures of [[Han Solo/Legends|Han Solo]]. One of these was ''[[Eight for Aduba-3: The Saga of the Starhoppers]]'', telling the Corellian's adventures on [[Aduba-3/Legends|Aduba-3]].

